I want to study social work to help children who are abused or neglected. I want to work with the Division of Family and Children Services. These children need someone to care for them. I want to help them and their families.

Important values for social workers are service, respect, and being honest. These values are also important to me. I want to help people and their families. I want to be kind and fair.

I wanted to help others, but I was not sure what job I wanted to do. I studied psychology in college. I wanted to understand people and their problems. After I graduated, I visited a friend who had a sixteen-year-old son. He was scared and unhappy because his parents were being mean to him. I talked to the police and told them I could help. They asked me to talk to the parents. I met with them and expressed my concerns. They did not want to listen.

This experience made me want to work with people who are hurt by their families. I want to help children who are in difficult situations.

I also believe in social justice. People say that every person is important. But sometimes we try to be like everyone else. I do not want to be like everyone else. I want to be myself. I have shown this by being different in my own way. I have colored my hair, worn clothes that fit me, and spoken out against unfair things.

I will continue to fight for what is right. I want to work with people who are hurt and help them to be happy and safe. I will be a good social worker because I care about people and want to help them.

This paper looks at two ways to understand sleep disorders. One model is called the biological model. It looks at genetics, health, and body functions. The other model is called the sociocultural model. It looks at how the environment and personal characteristics affect sleep disorders.

The biological model says that sleep disorders can be caused by genetics, medical problems, and the way our bodies work. It also looks at how our brain and body respond to sleep and wakefulness. A study on mice found that a special group of brain cells, called orexin, help control sleep and wakefulness. These cells have special receptors that help us sleep. If these receptors do not work well, it can cause problems with sleep.

Another study found that a medicine called baclofen can help people sleep. This medicine works by helping the brain cells that control sleep. This study shows that there is a connection between genetics and sleep. It also shows that problems with brain cells can cause sleep disorders.

The sociocultural model looks at how the environment and personal characteristics affect sleep disorders. It looks at things like where we live, how much money we make, and our skin color. For example, people who have a hard time sleeping might be more likely to have a hard time concentrating or doing their job. This can affect many parts of their life.

The sociocultural model also looks at how sleep disorders are related to other mental health problems. For example, people with depression or anxiety might have trouble sleeping. This can make their mental health problems worse.

In this paper, we will look at research on insomnia, which is a type of sleep disorder. We will also look at how the biological and sociocultural models relate to insomnia.

Insomnia is a sleep disorder that can be caused by many things, including genetics, medical problems, and the way our bodies work. It can also be caused by stress, anxiety, and other mental health problems. There are different types of insomnia, including primary insomnia and sleep disorders related to other mental health problems.

The primary sleep disorders include insomnia, hypersomnia, narcolepsy, and other sleep disorders. Insomnia is a problem with falling asleep or staying asleep. Hypersomnia is a problem with staying awake. Narcolepsy is a problem with falling asleep during the day.

Parasomnias are another type of sleep disorder. They are problems with sleep that cause behavioral or physical problems. For example, sleepwalking, nightmares, and sleep terrors are all parasomnias.

The biological model says that insomnia is caused by problems with the brain and body. The sociocultural model says that insomnia is caused by environmental and personal factors. Both models are important for understanding insomnia and finding ways to treat it.

This paper talks about Central Auditory Processing Disorder (CAPD). First, we will explain what CAPD is. Next, we will talk about how to diagnose it. Finally, we will discuss how a teacher can help a student with CAPD in a regular classroom.

CAPD is a problem with how the brain uses sound. It means the brain does not work well with the sounds we hear. People with CAPD can hear normally. They are not deaf. But their brain has trouble separating sounds and understanding them. For example, they may have trouble hearing in a noisy room or understanding what someone is saying when there is background noise.

CAPD was first identified in the 1950s. Researchers were studying children with communication problems. They developed tests to identify CAPD in the 1950s and 1960s. A conference in 1977 made researchers look closer at CAPD.

People with CAPD have trouble with many things. They may not know where sounds are coming from. They may have trouble hearing two sounds at the same time. They may not understand sound patterns. They may not know when someone is being sarcastic. They may have trouble hearing one sound when another sound is louder. They may not be able to understand what sounds mean. They may have trouble hearing sounds in the right order.

To diagnose CAPD, doctors and specialists use tests. They watch how the person acts and responds to sounds. They may use questionnaires and ask the person to do certain tasks. There is no one test that works all the time, and we do not know what causes CAPD.

A teacher in a regular classroom can help a student with CAPD. They can provide extra help with listening and understanding. They can use tools like headphones to help block out background noise. They can also help the student practice listening and following directions. The teacher can work with the student to make sure they understand what they are saying. They can also help the student find ways to stay focused and pay attention.

The play Twelfth Night says that using a disguise can be useful for hiding the truth, but it can also cause problems. If you keep using a disguise, you may lose your true self. A problem with stopping a lie is that you may hurt the people around you. Some people will not be angry, but others will be upset.

Deception about gender roles is a big problem. It raises many questions. Why do people want to hide their true selves and pretend to be the opposite sex? In the play, Viola pretends to be a man to protect herself. She feels safe in this way. But her disguise makes it hard for her to be with her friends and family. It also causes confusion. Olivia thinks Viola is a man, and falls in love with her. Viola also has feelings for Prince Orsino, but she hides them.

Twelfth Night shows how deception can help people understand their true feelings. Olivia and Prince Orsino may have hidden desires. When Viola pretends to be a man, they have to deal with their feelings. But it is hard to know for sure what they feel. Olivia seems to like Viola because Viola is a man, but she also seems to care about her as a person. However, Olivia quickly stops loving Viola and starts to see her as a sister. This makes it hard to know what Olivia really feels.

The play Twelfth Night teaches us that hiding the truth can be complicated. It can hurt the people we care about and make it hard for us to know who we are.

The German colonial rule in Africa was known for being very harsh. One example is the genocide of the Ovaherero and Nama people in German South West Africa. However, the German colonial empire was not the same everywhere. Different parts of the empire had different rules and ways of governing. Education also varied from place to place.

In some parts of the empire, like German East Africa, the British found many educated and able to read Africans when they took over in 1919. German education in other colonies was also praised by writers at the time.

But South West Africa (now Namibia) was very different. The government did not help much with education for Africans. Instead, missionaries gave education to many Africans. The government did support education for Europeans in the colony. The government built schools for Europeans and helped the missionary schools. These decisions had a lasting effect on South West Africa.

Other German colonies had many educated Africans, but South West Africa had a very low number of educated people. Many people in the colony could not read or write. Several reasons caused these differences. This paper will look at these reasons and examine the views of the settlers and colonial leaders on African people.

There are many studies on education in the German colonial empire. Most of these studies were written in German and published a long time ago. They mainly described the educational systems in the colonies. Later studies compared the educational systems in different colonies and looked at specific parts of education. These studies showed that each colony had a different educational system. One important study is Cohen's work on education in South West Africa and East Africa. Cohen compared the two colonies and explained why their educational systems were different. He said the large number of white settlers in South West Africa was a main reason for its educational system.

South West Africa had a moderate climate, but a lot of the land was desert. Because of this, many white people lived in South West Africa. By 1913, over 15,000 white people lived there, while only 5,336 lived in the colony with the next largest number of white settlers, East Africa.

Heavy metal music is a very big group of music types. It has grown over the last 100 years and now includes many kinds. To make things more complicated, many of these kinds of music have smaller kinds within them. There are many kinds of heavy metal, such as rock, jazz, and folk music. But the kind of heavy metal that started 40 years ago is very special.

Heavy metal music is very emotional and shows a lot of feelings, mostly on the darker side. People started to use heavy metal to express their feelings and thoughts. It was very flexible and people could make their own kinds of heavy metal music. This led to many new kinds of heavy metal and even smaller kinds within those.

Now it is hard to say what heavy metal is. It has taken things from other kinds of music and made them its own. But to understand heavy metal, we need to know where it came from and why it is a movement.

Heavy metal is a movement that is known for its darkness. It has more sound, more loudness, more power, and more show. People in heavy metal bands are very good at playing their instruments, and it shows in their music. Heavy metal is also a movement that was influenced by drugs. In the 1970s, there was a time when people used a lot of drugs, and this led to the creation of crazy and new music. Heavy metal has many qualities that are very new to music, such as being very emotional and showing the darker side of feelings.

Many early heavy metal songs expressed the darker side of feelings. One example is the song Helter Skelter by the Beatles. This song was considered one of the first heavy metal songs. It was a response to a song by the Rolling Stones that was also very heavy and dark. The Beatles wanted to show that they could make music that was just as heavy as the Stones.

Henri Rousseau was a famous Post-Impressionist artist. He made a painting called The Dream in 1910. This painting shows a woman in a dreamland. It also shows Rousseau's own dreams and goals. He wanted to be recognized by other artists and people who love art. But he faced a big problem. He had to decide if he should paint like other artists or be different.

To understand The Dream, we need to know about Rousseau's life. He was born on May 21, 1844, in a town in northwest France called Laval. His father was a wealthy man who sold metal things. Rousseau grew up without learning art in school. He worked for the government until he was 40. He was a toll collector. People called him a customs inspector. This was not an art job, but Rousseau liked to paint.

Rousseau's first wife died when their eight children were small. He had only one child, a daughter named Julia, left. He was very sad. He started painting to feel better. Rousseau wanted to be a good painter. But he was different from other artists. He painted what he saw in his life, not what others liked.

Rousseau wanted to be accepted by the art world. He was older when he started painting, and many other artists were famous. He worked hard, but he did not get the recognition he wanted until later, when another famous artist, Matisse, was also becoming known. A writer said that Rousseau wanted to paint in a way that was very good, but not too interesting, so people would like him. Matisse, on the other hand, did not want to paint in a boring way. He wanted to be different.

Rousseau's painting The Dream shows his problem. He wanted to be accepted by the art world, but he also wanted to be himself. This is a big decision for any artist.

Many great thinkers think that ethics and beauty are connected. They think that truth and beauty are the same. This makes sense. We learn many things in life through education and experience. But when we think about ethics and beauty, we do not need to be taught. We know what is beautiful and what is right without being told.

We try to understand why something is beautiful or right. We study art and literature to know why something is good. But we cannot explain it in simple words. We say that something is beautiful or right, but we cannot say why.

We can talk about the colors and shapes in a painting, but it does not explain why it is beautiful. We can talk about the words in a story, but it does not explain why it is good. When we talk about what we like, we often say, "There's just something about it." This "something" is hard to explain.

I think that ethics and beauty are connected because they are both hard to explain. We feel them, but we cannot say why. This connection is strong when we think about literature. Literature is a way to say things that need to be said. It is a way to feel things deeply. We value literature because it helps us understand what is important.

Values are important in life. Literature helps us understand these values. It teaches us what is right and wrong. This is why literature is important to us.

The country of Germany today is strong. It is a united country with one special culture. This culture is seen in the cities of München near the Alps and Kiel near the Baltic Sea. The same culture is felt in the cities of Köln on the river Rhine and Dresden on the river Elbe.

Germany has a special history. The country comes from different groups of people. These groups came from different places. They have different cultures. Germania is the old name for the land of Germans. Scholars do not agree on how the name "Germany" came to be.

The Roman historian Tacitus said the name came from a group of people called the Tungrians. They were a Germanic tribe. They crossed the Rhine River and fought with the Gauls. The Roman leader Julius Caesar first used the word "Germanus" in his book about the war with the Gauls. He used it to talk about Germanic tribes that fought against him.

Julius Caesar got the word "Germanus" from the Gauls. The Gauls used it to talk about their neighbors. Some people think the word came from a spear called a "ger". The Gauls might have used this spear in battle. Others think the word came from the Old Irish word "garim", which means "to shout". This might mean the Germans were loud or noisy.

A long time ago, the Roman historian Tacitus wrote about the origins of the Germans. He said the Germans were an old group of people. They were not mixed with other groups of people. They lived in a wild country with hard weather. They were not easy to live among. But they were home.

The Romans did not want to live in Germany. They went to Germany to get things and to fight. They would sometimes send soldiers to Germany. But they would usually go back to Rome.

As the Germanic tribes appeared, they lived near the Roman Empire. They traded goods and worked in the Roman army. They helped the Romans in battle.

I looked down and saw nothing. My mind was empty. I did not think or feel anything. I just looked at the view in front of me. A picture was before my eyes, but I did not connect it to any idea or feeling. My thoughts came and went quickly. I was not thinking at all. It was like my mind was working on its own, not mine. 

I once got an art book called "The New Drawing on the Right Side of the Brain." I wanted to learn to draw. I had wanted to since I was six years old. The book teaches how to draw. It says to put a frame around the picture you want to draw. This makes the picture easier to see. 

At that moment, I could not think of this frame. I stood and looked at the bowl in front of me. It was too much to understand. I felt amazed and confused. I remembered that some artists, like Picasso, like Monet, created art in their own special way. If I wanted to be an artist, this was my chance. I thought my picture, "Work in Brown," was starting. 

I picked up my pencil, my mind worked hard to create. Water flowed, it was calm and smooth. Pieces of the bowl broke off and went away. My hand moved again, but this time it was to the toilet handle. I tried to make the brown thing go away, but it was stuck. I had a mop in my hand, my feet were apart, and my tie was tight. I frowned and looked at the dirty thing in the toilet. I wanted to get rid of it. I pulled the toilet paper and wrapped my hand in it. Then I put my hand in the water, like a mother putting a turkey in the oven.

Teenagers are dying behind the wheel. Several things make this a big problem for young American drivers. The National Institutes of Health say that one reason is that the teen brain is not ready for driving dangers. Simple lack of experience is also a big part of the problem. This inexperience causes more accidents and more car rollovers, speeding, and driving off the road.

Teenagers also do worse when they drive with friends. Many people know that teenagers often drive with friends. A study by the Southern California Injury Prevention Research Center found a strong connection: between the age of the passenger and the number of traffic accidents.

California and other states try to make driving safer for teenagers by giving them temporary licenses that limit the hours they can drive and do not allow other minors as passengers.

But I think these licenses are only a temporary solution. The real problem is that young drivers are not good at handling driving risks and responsibilities. Psychologist Marvin Zuckerman says that 18 is too young to get a full driver's license. USA Today reports that Zuckerman has done research that shows many people under 20 like to take risks for the fun of it. It makes sense to delay driving until this tendency to take risks has gone down. If we keep giving driver's licenses to young teenagers, we will keep seeing many accidents and the number of deaths will be very high. By 2010, babies born during the Baby Boom will be old enough to drive and many new teen drivers will be on the road.

Legislation to fix this problem would be easy to understand. Schools could teach driver's education classes to begin learning to drive. But no one under 18 could drive a car. A temporary permit could still be given before a full driver's license. A certain number of hours of practice driving with a teacher would still be required. This number could be the same as what most states require now (in California, for example, that number is 6 hours of practice with a teacher and 50 hours of practice with an adult). Since many accidents happen in many states, national legislation would be a good way to protect teenagers across the country.

This idea is not new.

I looked at films from the Library of Congress. They have a collection of early movies made by Thomas Edison. I wanted to see all the movies that used tricks. There were fifteen of them from 1895 to 1901. These films use tricks to create illusions. I studied these films to understand their special effects.

Most of these films are set in a fixed place and use only one angle. The camera does not move when filming. The films use long and medium shots. They follow the rule that one shot is one film. However, some early movies broke this rule.

A special thing about these films is that they are set inside a fixed frame. The camera does not move from its position. This style comes from theater and magic shows. Because of this style, the actors do not move towards or away from the camera. They only move side to side. In the film "Uncle Josh in a Spooky Hotel," the actors enter and leave from the right side and move back and forth.

These films also use long shots and sometimes medium shots. Close-up shots are not used in any of these Edison films. This is because the audience sees the whole performance, like in a theater or a magic show. The actors do not move towards the camera, so close-ups are not used.

Most of these early films are short, about a minute long. They show simple tricks like magic and disappearing. However, some films are made with many physical shots joined together to create an illusion. Look at the film "The Execution of Mary, Queen of Scots" from 1895. At first, it seems like one shot, but it is actually several shots joined together.

John Taylor of Caroline was a man who liked liberty. He was a farmer and a politician. He was known for his strong ideas about freedom and government. Taylor thought the best kind of work is farming. This made him think about the government in a special way.

Taylor believed America had a chance to make a perfect system. There was no old tradition to stop the people making the government. This meant they could create a system where the people are in charge.

Taylor believed people have rights. These rights are important and must be protected. He thought if one right is taken away, all rights are in danger. He wanted the government to respect these rights. Taylor said the world is not always kind to people. But in a civilized society, this is not right.

Taylor wanted a government that understands people are good and bad. He thought a government should protect what is good and stop what is bad. He said a government is like people. It has good and bad qualities.

Taylor thought a good government should protect private property and help farmers. He also thought a government should not help rich people at the expense of others. He believed self-interest is a natural part of people. But it is bad when it hurts others. A good government can keep this from happening.

Taylor wanted a small Federal government. The government should only have the powers given to it in the Constitution. He thought a big government is expensive and can be cruel. But he also thought a simple reading of the Constitution can be wrong. He wanted to understand the ideas behind the Constitution.

Taylor thought the Declaration of Independence is very important. It says the United States is a group of states, not one country. He believed this was a very good idea.

There was a big drop in people submitting information about how they commute. This was a problem in the third month of the project. It was hard to know why this happened. People might have stopped commuting on foot or by bike because of cold winter weather. It also happened when students were busy finishing schoolwork before the holiday break. The holiday season was coming, and many students were not coming to school. This made it hard for them to fill out the commuter form. Even after the holidays, classes did not start again until late January. This might have caused the low number of submissions in February. It's also possible that people get excited about new projects at first, but then they lose interest. We tried to keep people interested by making a special challenge in March. This helped increase submissions for that month.

Another problem we faced was that people like to drive their cars. This is a big part of our culture. To encourage people to use other ways to commute, we gave prizes like gift certificates to restaurants and stores. We thought it would be interesting to see if bigger prizes would help. For example, we could have given away a new bike or a hybrid car. This might have helped people stay interested in the project. The prizes we gave out did not change much during the project. We thought about increasing the value of the prizes as time went on. Maybe this would have helped more people participate.

An ETF, or exchange traded fund, is a security that tracks a group of things, like an index fund. But it is more flexible and trades like a stock on an exchange.  It gives you the benefits of an index fund and the freedom of single stock ownership.  You can sell short, buy on margin, and buy as few as one share.

This is attractive, but there are some downsides.  You have to pay a commission for each trade, just like you would for a stock.  Another benefit is that there are many types of ETFs available.

But is this really true?  Let's look at a specific ETF, IHF, and its top 10 holdings.  These holdings make up 63.58% of the total assets.  We will compare the performance of these 10 stocks to the entire ETF.

To do this, we will look at the current percentage of each stock in the ETF.  We will use this to calculate the Beta and return of a portfolio made up of just these 10 stocks.  The chart below shows these calculations.

The results show that a portfolio of just the top 10 holdings would have a 6.11% higher return than the ETF, or a 16% increase in returns.  It also has a lower Beta, meaning it is less volatile.  But is this difference real, or just a coincidence?

To answer this, we will look at the standard deviation of each of the top 10 stocks.  We will compare this to the standard deviation of the entire ETF.  This will tell us if the difference between the two portfolios is statistically significant.

American writer Edgar Allan Poe wrote a famous poem. The poem is called "Dream-Land." "Dream-Land" is one of Poe's best poems. Poe used a word called "Thulé" in "Dream-Land." He got this word from a man named Virgil. Virgil used the word to describe a place north of Britain. The Greeks thought this place was the end of the world.

Poe liked reading German authors. A man named Karl J. Arndt wrote a book about Poe and another author named Goethe. Arndt said Poe's poem and Goethe's poem are very similar. This means Poe might have been copying Goethe.

Goethe was a famous writer. He wrote a play called "Faust." The play was published in two parts. The first part came out in 1808, and the second part came out in 1832 when Goethe died. Inside "Faust" is a short poem called "The King of Thulé." This poem is about a king who drinks a lot after his wife dies. He decides to die after throwing away a special cup.

Poe used the word "Thulé" in two of his writings. He used it once in "The Pit and the Pendulum" and twice in "Dream-Land." In "Dream-Land," Poe describes a place called Thulé as a dark, lonely place with no color. This is similar to Goethe's poem, where the king is also lonely and sad after his wife dies.

Goethe was a well-known author whom Poe would have respected. Poe admired another writer named Tennyson. Poe would have been familiar with Goethe's work because many people reproduced his writings after he first published them.

Can a customer get money from a store because the store manager did a bad thing on purpose?  Jennifer Palmer fell on an applesauce spill at a grocery store. She wants to show the store manager, Paul Martin, acted very badly because he was eating dinner and did not clean the spill for 30 minutes after he was told twice.

A judge will not quickly throw out Jennifer Palmer’s claim for more money. To get this extra money, Jennifer must show that Paul Martin acted very badly on purpose. She will say that Martin should have known it was bad to not clean the spill. She will say this because many people slipped and fell on the same kind of spills at the store before she did.

Jennifer will also say that Martin acted very badly because he did not clean the spill even after he was told about it twice. Paul Martin said he was eating dinner and did not have time to deal with customer complaints. He said the same thing when he was told again about the spill. On this day, Jennifer fell and was hurt very bad.

There were five other times when people slipped and fell at the store in the year 2009. Now Jennifer is suing the store for money because she is hurt. We are looking at if we should ask the judge to throw out the extra money she is asking for.

In California, a person can get extra money if the other person did something bad on purpose, or if they did something very bad by mistake. The law says this is true if the person did something ‘despicable’ and knew it would hurt someone. A court said that a person acts badly when they do something on purpose to hurt someone, or when they do something very bad and know it will hurt someone, but do nothing to stop it.

In this case, Jennifer will say that Paul Martin acted badly because he knew it would hurt someone if he did not clean the spill. He knew this because many people slipped and fell before, but he did not do anything to stop it.

Four years ago, I studied Islam at CBC.  A main topic of discussion was whether Islam is a hostile religion.  I think this question is still important today.  After 9/11, I saw the media's view of Islam change.  In 2001, a presidential candidate with a Muslim background like Barack Obama could not have been elected.  Now, the media is very tolerant of Islam in America.

The life of the Prophet Muhammad is interesting.  I learned about Muhammad's life, but I thought it was different from what I knew.  I believed Muhammad forced people to become Muslims.  He conquered tribes and made them join Islam.  But the biography says Muhammad was a kind person who was misunderstood.  People came to him because they liked his teaching.

I also see similarities between the life of Jesus and the miracles of Muhammad.  One example is when Muhammad multiplied food so there was enough for many people.  This style of writing makes me think the writers wanted Muhammad to be seen as a humble prophet.  I think this is wrong because it takes away from the life of Jesus.

Some stories in the biography are not from people who saw things happen.  They heard from others who heard from others.  This makes the stories seem less true.  I do not like this.  I think the biography tries to make Muhammad a great and humble person.  But history says he was not that way.

I do not like this biography because it does not show the truth about Muhammad.  I think Muslims today should know the real history of Muhammad's life.

Christianity spread quickly after Jesus died. But soon, people started to change his teachings. They added new ideas to his message. Over time, Christianity became very different from what Jesus taught. This is a common history. Many people still follow the old ways, but not many. They will not stop the change that is happening. In the future, there will be more understanding of Christianity's past. Many people will want to know what Jesus really said. They will try to remove the extra ideas that were added to his message. This will be a big change. The church will still be strong, but people's thoughts and actions will become more alike. There will be less difference between groups of Christians. This has happened before. The Romans used to be against Christians, but later they became Christian too. Our country used to treat African-Americans unfairly, but now they have leaders. A big change will happen in the Christian church. It will go back to its start. People will read Jesus' words in a new way. They will not take them as true stories. This will make it possible for the change to happen.

People who study history know that there was only one main idea - Judaism - before the Christian church. By the time the Romans controlled Jerusalem, the basic ideas of Christianity were already there. Many Jews were not alike. They were divided into groups. There were Sadducees, Pharisees, Essenes, Zealots, and many other ordinary people.

I think The Jungle shows that people are naturally selfish. They only want what is good for themselves, not others. The Jungle shows this in many ways. The people who own and run big factories only want to make their businesses bigger and wealthier. They do not care about anyone or anything that gets in their way. Upton Sinclair wrote about the damage pollution from these factories is causing. The factories are harming people and animals. The owners do not care about this.

The owners and managers also do not care about the workers. They make the workers work long hours and do not pay them well. When the companies need to, they fire many workers without warning. In the time when the book is set, there were no laws to protect workers. This allowed the owners to treat the workers badly.

The workers lived and worked in terrible conditions. They had to work hard and live in bad areas. There were no groups to help the workers. Some groups, called unions, were formed, but they often helped the owners more than the workers. The workers were treated very badly and had no way to escape the bad system.

Sinclair says that the workers were like slaves. They were very poor and had to wait for the owners to decide their fate. This made it hard for them to be good people.

Many writers use different methods to give readers a certain feeling or opinion about important subjects. These methods are not all the same. F. Scott Fitzgerald uses many of these methods in his novel, "The Great Gatsby." He sometimes uses words in a special way to give readers a certain feeling. He does this by using an adjective and a noun together that are not usually together. Other times, he uses a symbol to mean something, and then uses it for the same thing.

Fitzgerald uses this last method with many colors. He gives meaning to red, pink, white, and gray. In his book "The Great Gatsby," Fitzgerald creates meaning for colors, especially white and gray. He then uses this meaning to give readers a feeling about something.

The meaning Fitzgerald gives to white and gray is that they are the same. White is a little better and more upper class. Gray is a little older and faded. Fitzgerald shows this meaning at the start of the novel. He uses both colors a lot. Everyone is always wearing white. Daisy and Jordan are always dressed in white. Even Nick wears white clothes to Gatsby's party. But when Nick is not at Gatsby's party, the colors are different. He sees "primary colors" everywhere.

Fitzgerald makes white and gray clearer by using these colors in everyday things. He describes important and unimportant things with these colors. He says Nick walks "down white chasms of lower New York." He also says the names of people at Gatsby's party are "gray names." This helps readers see the meaning of white and gray.

Fitzgerald also uses white and gray to describe people and places. He says Jordan and Daisy had a "white girlhood" together. There are "gray cars" and "gray land" in the valley of ashes. He describes a child in the railroad as "gray" and a man as "gray old." After he gives meaning to white and gray, he uses them to say that something is not important or not special. He starts this with Daisy. He describes her as "dressed in white" and driving a "little white roadster." This makes her seem less important.

Fitzgerald uses more of this technique around Daisy to make her seem like a not important person. He says there is a "gray haze of Daisy's fur collar" and she is wearing a "white" dress. He uses colors to give readers a feeling about something long before he uses them again.

San Diego County is a great place for farming. The climate is good for growing many kinds of food. The land is used for many crops, including tomatoes, oranges, leafy green vegetables, squash, broccoli, herbs, peaches, lemons, and berries. People want to buy food from farms that do not use chemicals. Many farmers in the area offer tours of their farms and let people walk or hike on their land.

Organic farming helps the environment. It has more plant and animal life because it does not use chemicals. But organic farming is harder work and can be more expensive than farming with chemicals. Farmers must work harder to get rid of insects and weeds and to make the soil healthy. They may also lose more crops than farmers who use chemicals. A small organic farm is not as efficient as a big farm.

The land I chose is 160 acres near the town of Potrero in San Diego County. The land is near a forest and has chaparral, grass, and oak trees. Many animals and plants live in this area. Some animals are in danger of disappearing, like the kangaroo rat and the mountain yellow-legged frog. The government has a plan to protect this area.

People have lived in this area for a long time. The original owners of this land used it for cattle and wood. Today, a small farmer could get help from the government to make farming easier and more environmentally friendly. I looked at a real estate website and found a farm in the same area. The farm is organic and lets people visit and walk on the land.

Culture is very important in any negotiation. It can be hard to understand because it is not the same everywhere. We often think of culture as one thing, but it is not. It is made up of many different parts. We should not say that one group of people is the same. For example, all Russians are not alike. They are not all stubborn. And all Japanese are not the same. They are not all accommodating.

When we try to understand a new culture, we must learn about its history and its values. We must also try to understand its ways of thinking. We should not try to change the culture. We should just accept it for what it is. This is especially important in business. If we come to a meeting with a weaker position, we must be respectful of the other culture.

Culture is not just about countries. Companies also have their own culture. This can be seen in how people dress, how they talk, and how they work. Some companies work long hours, while others have a more relaxed schedule. Some companies encourage giving to charity, while others do not.

It is also important to understand the values of a culture. Values tell us why people act in certain ways. In some cultures, it is very important to save face. This means that people will not make their company or boss look bad, even if it means not getting what they want. In other cultures, people will work hard to get a good deal. These values are important to know before a negotiation.

But it is also important to get to know the person you are negotiating with. This can help you understand their values and what they want. With this knowledge, you can have a more effective negotiation.

In the book of the Bible, Psalm 14, it says: “The fool hath said in his heart, ‘There is no God.’” This idea is also in the writing of Thomas Aquinas. We want to compare their thoughts on God. But first, we must agree that they both believe in one God, the God of the Bible. If we think about another kind of God, we cannot compare their ideas. So we will assume they both believe in this one God.

Thomas Aquinas and St. Anselm write to prove that God exists. But we think neither of them gives a complete reason to believe in God. To show why, let us first look at St. Anselm's idea.

St. Anselm says we can find God in our own minds. We cannot think of God not being real. He says to look inside ourselves for proof of God's existence. St. Anselm thinks this is enough. We do not need evidence from outside ourselves to know God exists. This idea is called faith.

St. Thomas Aquinas has a different idea. He says we can prove God exists using reason and evidence we can see. We do not need faith. He thinks this idea will help people join the Christian church. It makes it easier to convince them to join without needing them to believe something they cannot prove. St. Thomas gives five reasons to show God exists: change, cause-and-effect, things that exist and do not exist, degrees of good and bad, and harmony. He thinks these reasons are so strong they show God must exist.

A long time ago, in the fifth or sixth century BCE, a prince was born. He would one day be known as Buddha. He gave up his life in the world and became a wise man. His teachings made Buddhism. This religion is around 2,500 years old. It looks different now than it did when Buddha was alive. This can be seen in the country of Sri Lanka. They have a special ceremony every year. Monks and people who are not monks participate in this ceremony. It is important to them, even though Buddha did not teach about any celebration like this. These changes are small and big. They change the way people live Buddhism.

Some words will be used a lot in this talk. There is a big difference between internal and external. An internal force is something that comes from people who follow Buddhism, no matter if they are monks or not. An external force is something from people who are not Buddhists. A hostile force is something that hurts or wants to hurt Buddhists. It is not good for the Buddhist community. A benign force is something that does not want to hurt or help the Buddhist community. It may help or hurt by accident.

First, let's talk about the basics of Buddhism. Buddhists believe in three important things: the Buddha, the Dhamma, and the Sangha. The Dhamma is all the Buddhist teachings. These teachings are in three baskets: the Tripitaka. One basket has all the stories of the Buddha. One basket has the rules for living. One basket has the deep ideas of Buddhism. These ideas are that there is no soul, that life is suffering, and that everything is not permanent. People must understand these ideas to stop the cycle of death and rebirth. When people understand, they will not be controlled by desire, hatred, and misunderstanding. In Buddhism, there are rules for how to live. For people who are not monks, there are five rules: do not kill, do not lie, do not steal, do not have sex with someone you should not, and do not take drugs. For monks, there are many more rules to follow. The most important idea in Buddhism is the four noble truths. First, life is suffering. Second, attachment causes suffering. Third, suffering can be overcome.

The United States and Mexico are two countries that had a long rivalry lasting 57 years, from 1836 to 1893. They clashed on many issues, including their feelings about religion and culture. They also had problems with disagreements about land and interests. 

This is like other countries that have a long rivalry with a neighbor. Countries that share a border often disagree on important issues. The US and Mexico are like other countries that have a long rivalry with a neighbor. A man named David M. Pletcher said that the US had big problems with Mexico and Cuba for a long time. Both of these countries are close to the US, and they have been rivals.

The US and Mexico had problems because of their different religions. In the past, Americans did not like Catholicism and monarchical systems. This made it hard for the US and Mexico to be friends. The US and Mexico did not trust each other because they both learned from their former rulers. The English and Spanish had a lot of distrust, and this was passed down to the US and Mexico.

The countries had 17 arguments between 1836 and 1893. Most of these arguments were about land. There were many problems on the border, like raids by bandits and outlaws. The US and Mexico had to use military force to stop the problems. 

As time passed, Mexico became more dependent on the US. This helped to reduce the rivalry. Later, the US changed its goals and started to help Mexico economically. This helped to end the rivalry between the two countries.

Fifteen years ago, I became suddenly and unexpectedly sick with a disease I did not know existed.

I was a nurse at the time. I became a nurse for safety and security because I did not have it as a child. People said, "You will always find work because people will always get sick." 

So, I became a nurse instead of my dream job as a scientist or journalist. I worked hard, but at 46 years old and alone, I could not work anymore. I have no money. I get by, but every day is a struggle. I am grateful to my family and friends who help me.

My point is that bad things can happen to anyone at any time. There are no guarantees. Some problems are too big to solve alone.

I agree that we should not rely too much on big government. But I think it is better to trust and help each other than to be alone. Americans used to help each other and ask for help. This is how our country grew.

Some people talk about rugged individualism, but our ancestors did not make it alone. They helped each other and shared what they had.

So, be prepared. I have a disaster kit and first aid supplies. But it is also important to know your neighbors. They may help you in hard times. If you have a farm, it is a good idea to be able to make your own food. But do not forget to know the people around you.

Many questions have been asked about how living things change over time. Why do they change in the way they do? Are there rules that limit how they change? In 1917, a scientist named D'Arcy Thompson said we do not yet understand even the simplest shapes of living things. This is still true today. More recently, people have used math to study how certain animals grow their shells. Our study is looking at how math can help us understand how living things change over time.

We are studying a group of animals called Prunum. We are using math to model how they grow their shells. We took pictures of Prunum shells and used them to create a model. We entered the model into a computer program called CerioShell. This program helps us see how the shells might have looked in the past or in the future.

A shell is like a long tube that grows over time. It turns in a circle as it grows. This circle is made up of many parts called whorls. A whorl is like a ring on the shell. The shell grows around a center point called the columella. The center of each whorl is connected to the next one by a line called a suture.

The shell has an opening at one end called the aperture. The shell grows faster in some places than in others. We can count the whorls by looking at the shell from the top and counting the lines where the shell grows.

We can also think of the shell as a path that the animal follows as it grows. We can use math to map this path. Once we have the math, we can change the model to see what the shell might look like in the future.

Indonesia has a big problem. Many babies and mothers do not live. This is a big problem in Indonesia for ten years. The country is getting better in some areas, like water and sanitation. But it is not getting better fast enough in child and mother health.

We will talk about why this is happening. We need to make the health system stronger. We cannot just use programs to fix the problem.

Indonesia is getting better in one area. Now 72% of babies are born with a healthy worker there. But this number includes traditional workers who may not be able to help if there is a problem. Many mothers die from bleeding during pregnancy.

We also see a problem with children's health. Fewer children are getting help for diarrhea. We do not have much information about how mothers are taken care of after they have babies. This is a big concern.

Only 4% of babies are born through a special kind of delivery called a c-section. This is not good. The rate is much higher in cities than in the countryside. This means some people have no access to good healthcare. The rich have access to more healthcare than the poor. This is not fair.

We want to know how to make things better. Should we make special programs for babies and mothers or should we make the whole health system stronger? One way is to make special programs. This way is good because it is easy to see what we are doing and it can help people faster. But it has some problems. We may not have enough money or workers for other health problems. We may also have too many programs that are not working well together.

Victorian novels are known for careful details and a focus on the rich people in that time. Two novels that are Victorian, but are different from others, are Oliver Twist and Wuthering Heights. These two novels use mystery and strange situations, which are not typical of the time. These strange events help show the feelings and thoughts of the characters.

The characters in these novels often use dreams or feel like they are dreaming. In Oliver Twist, strange things happen to show what Oliver is feeling inside. When Oliver is shot, he remembers it in a dream-like way. This shows that he had no control over what happened to him. He was in a lot of pain and scared.

In the passage, Oliver sees his enemies, Sikes and Crackit. He is still talking to them, but they are arguing. Then, he hears shots and sees lights. He is moved away quickly. He feels a lot of pain.

In these scenes, Dickens shows that Oliver had no control over his life. He was in a difficult situation. He had to accept that he could not change what happened. This scene shows that Oliver was giving up.

Wuthering Heights also uses strange and dream-like scenes. In one scene, there is no day and night. It is a very quiet and short night. It seems like the night is long because it is so quiet. But it is also short because it does not last long.

In both novels, these strange events help the readers understand the characters better. They show the characters' thoughts and feelings. These scenes make the characters more real and interesting.

I worked with students in an after-school program two years ago. I helped them with their schoolwork, but my strengths were in English and reading. One boy, named Adrian, was having trouble reading. He was in third or fourth grade. I thought something was not right. He could read some words, but not others. He was Latino, but spoke perfect English. We worked together until I met his mother. She did not speak English. We used simple words to talk.

I understood then that Adrian knew some words, but not the English alphabet. I think this is a big problem in schools, especially in California. A child can speak perfect English, but still have trouble reading. I think we can all agree that this is a problem.

I want to tell you about Adrian to show that this problem is not always easy to see. We need to help children who do not know the alphabet. One way to do this is to teach them in their own language and English. This is called a dual language system. It is very good for all children.

Some people are afraid of this system. They think it is a waste of money and that most children will not benefit. But this is not true. If we use this system in all classrooms, all children will benefit.

We do not need to teach all teachers two languages. This is not realistic. But we can have special helpers who are bilingual. They can help teachers and students.

This is one way to solve the problem of reading in schools. We need to work together to help all children read.

Many people think there is something bigger than they are. They go to school to learn about it. Some people go to church or temple. Others think about it on their own. Most of us learn about religion from our parents. But some people do not believe in it. They think there is nothing beyond what we can see and feel. They may change their ideas about what is important to them. Everyone has their own way of thinking about spirituality.

I asked my father about his favorite bird. We sat on our porch and listened to the rain. The water from the roof made the plants on the porch wet. My father looked out at the rain. He seemed to be thinking about something. He was thin and his hair was thinning. I felt sad and scared. I did not talk to him about how much I would miss him. I hugged him and sat down next to him. We looked out at the rain together.

My father died five days after my twenty-second birthday. He had cancer. He had treatment, but it did not help. I did not want to watch him die. I did not want to see the life that made me end. I wanted to remember him for how he lived, not how he died. I went to my room for three days and waited for news.

No one called me.

The Gothic novel is a mix of old and new. This is what Ian Watt says in his book about the rise of the Gothic novel. Many people think that the Gothic mode is not real or not deep. But others like its "terrible sublime" part. The first Gothic novel was Horace Walpole's "The Castle of Otranto." It uses the ideas of both old and modern romances. 

Horace Walpole used old theatrical elements and new ideas to create a new way of writing. He called it "A Gothic Story." The Gothic genre uses old elements from medieval times. Even at the time "The Castle of Otranto" was published, the word "Gothic" was used to describe many things. People thought it was old-fashioned. 

The combination of the old and new is what makes the Gothic genre stay popular for a long time. It is both old and new to readers who are far from the original writing time. 

One of the main ideas in Gothic novels is chivalry. Chivalry is a medieval idea about how to train a knight. It is important to Gothic writers because it shows the kind of person they thought was ideal - brave, honorable, and good. 

Gothic writers used chivalric ideas and manners to make the past seem ideal and romantic. They wanted to improve the present. When Horace Walpole wrote "The Castle of Otranto," he was living in a time of trouble. He was unhappy about the future. He may have thought that the good qualities of people in the past had disappeared. 

In "The Castle of Otranto," a character named Frederic is like a knight from the past. He is a prince who has suffered and is brave. He is described in a way that shows he has many chivalric qualities. This makes him seem like an exaggerated version of a knight, which is a common idea in Gothic stories.

Supply chain management is the process of moving goods from the customer's order to the final customer. This process includes getting materials, making products, and delivering them to customers. The idea of supply chain management was first used in 1982 by a business consultant named Keith Oliver. He explained that supply chain management is a process that helps companies satisfy customers' needs quickly and efficiently. 

There are six key parts of supply chain management: production, supply, inventory, location, transportation, and information. Business managers use these parts to give the best service to their customers.

1. Production is the first step in the supply chain process. It is the base of the entire process. Managers need to know what customers want. They look at the market, which shows what customers demand. Then, they decide what products to make and how many to make. They also decide where to make the products and which factory will work best.

2. The second key part is supply. This is the process of making decisions about the skills and partners a company needs. A company may have many parts that make different products. The manager decides which part is best for each job. They may also decide to work with other companies to make some things. The reason for this is to make the process faster and cheaper.

3. Inventory is the third key part. This is the stock of products that a company has. Managers need to make sure they have the right amount of products for customers.

4. Location is the fourth key part. This is where the products are made and stored.

5. Transportation is the fifth key part. This is how the products are moved from the factory to the customer.

6. Information is the sixth key part. This is the data that managers use to make decisions about the supply chain.

Managers use these six key parts to provide the best service to their customers. They make sure to plan and control each step of the process carefully. If they do not, it can cost them a lot of time and money in the long run. For example, big companies like Wal-Mart and Target have a clear plan for every part of their business. This helps them work smoothly and avoid confusion.

People are saying Hitler is alive in Burma. 

Ellen Page, the actress from the movie “Juno,” stands on a street corner with a big sign. The sign says, “Hitler is alive in Burma.” Burma is a country in Southeast Asia. A bad group of people, the military, is in charge. They took control of the country in 1962. In 2007, people began to protest against the group. Many monks were leaders of the protests. People started to join in, and at first, the military let them protest. But then the violence started. The military attacked the monks and their homes. They arrested journalists who were reporting on the protests. A Japanese journalist named Kenji Nagai was killed for reporting on the protests. Many people were hurt or killed.

This is not new. Many governments throughout history have tried to stop people from speaking out against them. In ancient Rome, the leaders thought they were gods. In Japan, the leaders believe they are gods too. In the United States, the president, George W. Bush, talked to a man named Ted Haggard.

There have been many bad things that have happened. In 1989, many people went to Tiananmen Square in China to protest against the government. The Chinese government said few people were killed, but other groups said many more people died. In Rwanda, a group of people killed many others, including those who were not part of their group. Hitler and his friends killed many Jewish people.

These are just a few examples. Many governments have tried to control their people. But people will always speak out against injustice.

Duke Ellington is a great jazz musician because he worked for a long time and made many good songs. His music has a special quality because he knew how to make his band sound good together. He was a good composer. He wrote music that showed the special talents of each musician in his band. Ellington created the structure for his musicians to play freely, and he also wrote music that was tightly organized and had a special style.

Duke Ellington was very good at writing music that had a good tone. He knew how to make his band sound good together, and he made sure each musician had a special part in the music. He made many great songs that are still popular today.

One of his first big songs was called "Creole Love Call." It was a slow blues song that had a call-and-response part for the singer and the reed instruments. The singer started smooth and then got louder and rougher. This song showed how Ellington used the singer's voice to make the music more interesting.

In another song, "Hot and Bothered," Ellington used his skill at organizing music to make a good sound. He used a special type of singing called "scat" to make the music sound richer. In "It Don't Mean a Thing (If It Ain't Got That Swing)," Ellington used a trombone player named Joe "Tricky Sam" Nanton to make the music sound good.

Ellington's music is special because he knew how to make each musician sound good and how to make them sound good together. He was a very good composer, and his music is still popular today.

When Patricia Neal was fourteen, she felt something was missing. She didn't know what it was, but she felt it. This feeling stayed with her for three years. At seventeen, she knew she wanted a person, not just a thing. But she didn't like any of the boys who liked her. Some tried to win her over, but it didn't work.

Patricia wondered what was wrong with her. She thought about this a lot. She didn't know what she wanted. Her parents were nice and calm. They never argued. But Patricia was not like them. She was lively and fun. She liked being different.

On this day, Patricia was not calm. She was looking for ideas. She heard a loud cry from the kitchen. She ran to see what was wrong. Her mother was on the ground, hurting. Patricia helped her mother up and got her to the car. Her mother told her to take her to the hospital.

At the hospital, Patricia helped her mother into a bed. Then she waited for the doctors. They came and looked at her mother. Patricia was very worried. She had fallen off a stool while reaching for a vase.

This study looked at how following a "Mediterranean Diet" (Med diet) can affect the risk of heart disease and stroke. The Med diet is a special kind of diet that includes a lot of plant food, like fruits, nuts, and whole grains, and is low in animal products and saturated fat.

Past studies have shown that people who follow the Med diet are less likely to die from heart disease and other types of cardiovascular disease. A study also showed that the Med diet is better than a low-fat diet for helping people lose weight and lower their bad cholesterol levels.

This study looked at 74,886 women between the ages of 38 and 63 who were part of a larger group of nurses. The women reported what they ate in six different questionnaires over 20 years. The researchers used this information to give each woman a score based on how well she followed the Med diet.

The researchers found that women who followed the Med diet more closely were less likely to get heart disease or have a stroke. They looked at how often women had heart disease, fatal heart disease, or a stroke over 20 years. They found that women who followed the Med diet closely were about 29% less likely to have heart disease or a stroke.

The researchers controlled for other factors that could affect the results, such as age, smoking, weight, and physical activity. They used a special kind of mathematical model to see how following the Med diet affected the risk of heart disease and stroke.

The results show that following the Med diet can help lower the risk of heart disease and stroke in women.

In 2007, a big problem happened in the United States. Many people lost their jobs, the housing market fell, and important companies were in trouble. This problem, known as a recession, continues today. We need to ask: how did this problem happen and how can we stop it? The answer is simple: the financial crisis was caused by bad and foolish decisions by politicians. They pushed banks and companies to lend money to people who could not pay it back. This was a big problem because the country's financial system was not strong.

Two big companies, Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac, were also in trouble. They helped to sell these bad loans to other companies. When people could not pay their loans, the banks were in trouble. They sold these bad loans to other companies, and the problem went to the whole country.

This problem started a long time ago, in 1999. The president at that time, Bill Clinton, wanted to stay in office. To make people like him more, he let banks lend money to people who could not pay it back. This made a big problem for the country.

A reporter, Steven Holmes, wrote about this in 1999. He said that Fannie Mae was under pressure to lend money to people who could not pay it back. He also said that this could lead to a big problem later. And it did.

Many things made this problem worse. New kinds of loans, such as adjustable-rate mortgages, were created. These loans were complicated and made it easy for people to borrow too much money. This made the housing market go up and down, and many people lost their homes.

The big banks had a lot of money tied up in these bad loans. When the housing market fell, they lost a lot of money. The top five banks in the United States had over $4 trillion dollars in bad loans in 2007. This was a very big problem. In the end, some of these banks went out of business, and the government had to take control of two of the biggest companies, Fannie and Freddie.

Exposition: the part of your story where you explain background information.  This can be boring.  Your readers want to get to the exciting parts.

Most writers know the rule "Show, don't tell."  But it's easy to make mistakes.  Dr. Merlin has trouble with too much information.  She sometimes forgets to make things happen.

Exposition is not your friend.  Instead of telling the readers what happened, you should show them.  In a movie, this means one character tells another a lot of information.  In a story, it means the writer does the telling.

For example, imagine a story where a woman loses her husband.  You wouldn't expect the whole story to be about the wedding and the husband's death.  You would want to know more about the husband and how he made the woman's life better.  You would want to feel sad when he dies and understand how she feels.

To do this, you need to add meat to the story.  This means showing the reader how the woman and her husband met, what they were like together, and how they felt about each other.  You need to give the reader clues about the woman's thoughts and feelings.

As a writer, it's hard to resist telling too much.  But you should remember that readers want to get to the exciting parts.  So, be careful with exposition.  Give your readers the meat they need to care about your story.

I watched two news programs from Columbus, Ohio. The first one was on NBC 4 this morning (August 13, 2011). The main story was about a man named Shad Hostettler. He is from Ashley, Ohio and hurt his wife. I did not hear her name. They showed his picture. He looked very bad. They gave this story only two minutes. I think they gave it enough time.

The second story was about a young man named Travis Buyers. He was 18 years old and was shot in the Sharon Woods area. He was hurt very badly. The police were still looking for the person who did this. This story was short. Maybe it was because the man who was shot is black. I have seen this before. When a white person is a victim, the news talks about it a lot. But when a minority person is a victim, the news does not talk about it as much.

The next story was about a helicopter that was shot. The police are looking for the person who did it. They think they know where the shot came from. If you have information, you can call the police.

The next story was about the weather. There will be rain and thunderstorms on Saturday. The weather will be hot.

They also talked about a robbery at a store on Clime Road in Columbus. The man who robbed the store is black. He was wearing a black sweatshirt. The police are looking for him.

They also talked about a man named Rene Rodriguez. He is a convicted criminal. He was involved in a big crime in Texas. He was sentenced to 25 years in prison. They called it 300 months. I do not know why they said that. They also said he is Hispanic. But that is not important to the story.

There is a strong connection between brothers. It is a connection that cannot be broken. Many feelings are inside this connection: love, pride, envy, and hurt. Brothers understand each other very well. They can see themselves in their brother. When trouble is great, the true nature of this connection shows. It is either good or bad. When these feelings are clear, they cause problems. Understanding the feelings between brothers means dealing with the problems they bring. When you look at your brother, you see yourself. You see yourself, not how others see you, but how you really are. Your actions and their results show what kind of person you are.

In the story "The Scarlet Ibis," two brothers look at this connection. They explore all the feelings that come with it. These two boys go on a journey through a beautiful and vivid place. Bitter sadness and great pride are mixed together in a big way. Only one brother lives in the end. The story shows the brother's feelings through the main character, Doodle, and how he acts. It also shows these feelings through the narrator, who sees the world in a certain way and is influenced by it.

The main character's actions are driven by one feeling: pride. From the start, when he and his little brother, Doodle, go out together, he feels unhappy with Doodle. He wanted a brother who could do things with him, like run and climb trees. But Doodle was not able to do these things because he was sick. The main character had big dreams, but they were crushed when he found out Doodle was sick. He even thought about hurting Doodle, which is not a good thing to think. But when Doodle smiles at him, he feels better. This shows that he really cares about his brother.

The human brain is a complicated machine. It helps us think and learn. Over time, people have used different pictures to describe how it works.  At first, it was compared to a piece of wax. Later, it was compared to a piece of paper. Then, it was compared to a book. Now, it is compared to a computer. But these pictures are not perfect.

The brain gets information from our senses. Our senses are our eyes, ears, mouth, and skin. They turn things like light, sound, and touch into signals. The brain uses these signals and changes them again and again. It does this in two ways. First, it looks at each small piece of information. Then, it uses what it already knows to help it understand.

For example, when you see a picture of a box, your brain first looks at the colors and where the edges are. It puts these small pieces together to decide what you are seeing. Then, it uses what it knows about boxes to help you understand it.

The brain also decides what information is important. It ignores some things, like the blades of grass when you look at your shoes. But it pays attention to things that are important, like your name when someone says it in a noisy room.

The brain needs to store information so it can use it later. There are three kinds of memory: what we see, what we work with now, and what we remember for a long time. First, we put the information into the brain. There are different ways to do this, depending on what kind of information it is.

After we store information, we need to keep it. Some studies on animals show that we use electricity to keep information in our brains for a short time. We also think that information we keep for a long time is stored in the shape of certain kinds of proteins.

There are many ways to think about how the brain organizes information. Some people think about how we remember things. Others think about how computers work. Still, others think about what happens in the brain when we are alive. One way to think about it is to picture a network of connected ideas. For example, if you think about a chair, you might also think about a table and wood.

Aldous Huxley is worried about the future. He created a scary story called Brave New World. It is a warning about the dangers of a world where technology and money control people's lives. The people in this world value being part of a group over being an individual. They are taught from a young age to be happy and do not think about anything else. The citizens are like pawns in a game. They are controlled by a man called the World Controller. If we look closely at Huxley's book through the ideas of Marxism, we see that he does not like the way the world is going.

Huxley makes fun of capitalism in Brave New World. He uses the idea of "false consciousness." This means that people do not know how they are being controlled by the rich and powerful. They are too busy thinking about their own problems. The people in the story are conditioned to want to buy and spend money. This is controlled by the World Controller. The lower classes do not know they are being tricked. They are happy to buy things and have fun. The higher classes know what is happening, but they do nothing to stop it. Only a few people, like Bernard, try to change the system.

In Brave New World, people do not have real relationships with each other. The characters are not deep and interesting. Huxley might be saying that technology and capitalism are taking away people's free will and ability to express themselves. People do not feel real emotions like love. They only talk about superficial things, like how a person looks. This shows how capitalism is controlling people's lives. They are happy to be part of the group and do what they are told.

The people in the story are very happy to be where they are in the social hierarchy. This is like what the Marxists say happens to the working class. The working class is tricked into thinking they are better than others as long as they keep buying and obeying the rules. Huxley is warning us about the dangers of a world where people are controlled by money and technology.

I have been a student at University Park for about two and a half years. Getting around campus can be hard. My first year, I lived in a dorm called East Halls, which is very far from the center of campus. It took me 25 minutes to walk to some classes, especially on bad weather days. One of my teachers told me that not long ago, East Halls was far from campus with empty space all around it. Now, there are sports fields, new buildings, and apartments. As our campus gets bigger, it is harder to get from one place to another.

The best way to solve the problem of getting around is to use bicycles. But it is not just about having a bike. Students need to ride them, and the campus needs to be good for bicyclists.

I met a friend who started biking again after a few years. He said, "Bikes are great." They are good for your body, and they are the fastest way to travel. I live off campus, far from the center of campus. I have class in Thomas building, a 25-minute walk from my home. If I ride a bike, it takes only 5 minutes.

But there is a problem. Pollock Road is the best way to get to Thomas building, but it is not always easy. There are things to like about walking, but I am too busy to walk. If I didn't have a bike, I would have to walk to class. Walking would take 30-40 minutes one way, so that's over 2 hours a week. That's too much time for me.
